The paper discusses the use of text analysis to measure the tendency of nations to pursue novel ideas in biomedical research. This falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and digital libraries (cs.DL). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of machine learning techniques (cs.SI) and the analysis of scientific collaboration networks (cs.CY) which are also relevant sub-categories.
